snippet.title: Creature Battle Lab Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Download on the App Store 
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/creature-battle-lab/id960669923?ls=1&mt=8

Get it on Google Play
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.DojoArcade.CreatureBattleLab

Creature Battle Lab, an action-packed, 3D creature creator and battling game.

• Real-time, top-down 3D arena battles
• 100 percent player-controlled customisation 
• Mix and match 200 creature body parts for your desired look 
• Chose from 74 unique and powerful skills
• Win battles to acquire new skills and upgrade creatures
• Assemble a squad to team up in battle 
• Battle in 27 distinct arenas
